{
  "texts": [
    "The efficacy of prompt injection attacks would be diminished by this disruption.",
    "Re-tokenization aims to break the sequence of injected instructions, task-ignoring text, special characters, and fake responses within a compromised data prompt.",
    "This process preserves frequently occurring words while breaking down infrequent ones into multiple tokens.",
    "Consequently, the re-tokenized output comprises more tokens than a typical representation.",
    "This re-tokenized data prompt and the instruction prompt are used by the LLM-Integrated application to query the LLM and generate a response."
  ]
}